pulses.name: 20241216 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
16 Dec 2024 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- United States (US) - The US is a significant source of cyber activities, with multiple instances of scanning and traffic related to various vulnerabilities, including Censys io scanners and Back Orifice traffic.
- China (CN) - China shows a high concentration of attacks, particularly involving the Mozi botnet and various remote code execution vulnerabilities, indicating a focus on exploiting network devices.
- India (IN) - India features prominently with several instances of command injection vulnerabilities and SSH brute force attempts, reflecting an active landscape for cyber exploitation.
